OL,3,CAlmost #400,000 in compensation
OL,4,Cclaimed after summer riots on Teesside
OL,6,FAlmost #400,000 in compensation is
OL,7,Fbeing claimed in the Cleveland Police
OL,8,Farea following riots in Hartlepool and
OL,9,FMiddlesbrough over the summer.
OL,11,FCleveland Police and Crime
OL,12,FCommissioner Matt Storey told a
OL,13,Fmeeting that 39 claims have been
OL,14,Freceived so far for damage caused to
OL,15,Fbusinesses, cars and homes during
OL,16,Friots in Middlesbrough and Hartlepool,
OL,17,Faccording to the Local Democracy
OL,18,FReporting Service.
