OL,3,CAlmost #400,000 in compensation
OL,4,Cclaimed after summer riots on Teesside
OL,6,FThe riots on Teesside followed the
OL,7,Fstabbing of three girls in Southport,
OL,8,FLancashire on 29 July when
OL,9,Fmisinformation about the identity of
OL,10,Fthe assailant was spread online.
OL,12,FUnder the the Riot Compensation Act
OL,13,Fpeople can claim if they were not
OL,14,Fadequately covered by insurance for
OL,15,Fdamage, destruction or theft resulting
OL,16,Ffrom a riot.
OL,18,FInsurers are also able to make claims
OL,19,Ffor reimbursement after paying out on
OL,20,Finsurance policies that cover riot
OL,21,Fdamage.
