OL,6,FAccording to the Home Office
OL,7,Fsuccessful claims paid under the Act
OL,8,Fare paid from budgets allocated to
OL,9,Fpolice commissioners, or in some
OL,10,Finstances regional mayors.
OL,12,FMatt Storey has previously said that
OL,13,Fclaims, which have to be evidenced,
OL,14,Fwere being assessed and processed with
OL,15,Fnothing yet paid out.
